ğŸ† Blockchain Certificate Generator
The Blockchain Certificate Generator is a decentralized application (DApp) that allows authorized issuers to create and verify certificates using blockchain technology. It ensures security, transparency, and tamper-proof storage of digital credentials, eliminating the risk of forgery and providing permanent verification.

